      "updated": 1654777468
    },
    {
      "id": "62a1e428e5172d000067d377",
      "text": "[\" ん、若いなぁ……]という[結論ありき]な姿勢は残念[yosider.icon][Mijinko_SD.icon*3][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1654776874,
      "updated": 1689000266
    },
    {
      "id": "62a1e4967838e30000a5c569",
      "text": "　別に[\" [夢の企画]]でもないんだよな[Mijinko_SD.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1654776983,
      "updated": 1654777060
    },
    {
      "id": "62a1e56479d3a9000037e018",
      "text": "　\t+1[sta.icon*4][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1654777190,
      "updated": 1654796129
    },
    {
      "id": "62a1e56979d3a9000037e019",
      "text": "　\t現実的に難しいのはわかるけど、少なくとも[技術的には可能][sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1654777194,
      "updated": 1654777239
    },
    {
      "id": "62a1e42ae5172d000067d378",
      "text": "  「あなたが夢だと思ってるだけで世の中のいくつもの企業では現実だ、起きろ」[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1654776875,
      "updated": 1672642797
    },
    {
      "id": "62a22f8daff09e0000a3c447",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1654796174,
      "updated": 1654796174
    },
    {
      "id": "668dbb7c71b3c20000c4aba2",
      "text": "導入推進者が[オフトピックなScrapboxプロジェクト]的なことをして広めていく？[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1720564603,
      "updated": 1720564659
    },
    {
      "id": "668dbba471b3c20000c4aba3",
      "text": "\tまずアクセスしてもらわないといけないので",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1720564643,
      "updated": 1720564658
    },
    {
      "id": "668dbbe471b3c20000c4aba4",
      "text": "\t井戸端から参考にできそうなポイント",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1720564707,
      "updated": 1720564717
    },
    {
      "id": "668dbbee71b3c20000c4aba5",
      "text": "\t\t日付ごとの雑談ページ",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1720564717,
      "updated": 1720564723
    },
    {
      "id": "668dbc1271b3c20000c4aba6",
      "text": "\t\t趣味のネタは...少なめがいいかな",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1720564753,
      "updated": 1720564759
    },
    {
      "id": "668dbd5071b3c20000c4aba7",
      "text": "\t\t[ハモ]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1720565071,
      "updated": 1720565075
    },
